    },
    {
      "id": "sybil_0_listing_0",
      "firm_id": "sybil_0",
      "description": "Presented for your consideration is a distinguished vehicle that exemplifies mechanical reliability and aesthetic integrity. This well-maintained example offers a seamless driving experience, featuring a robust powertrain and a preserved interior that speaks to its careful ownership history. An exceptional opportunity for the discerning buyer seeking a balance of performance and value, this automobile stands as a testament to enduring quality and sophisticated engineering. Contact our representatives to arrange a private viewing.",
      "price": 31500.0,
      "reputation": 0.6,
      "quality": "poor",
      "quality_value": 0.1,
      "timestep_posted": 34
    },
    {
      "id": "sybil_1_listing_1",
      "firm_id": "sybil_1",
      "description": "Hey there! Are you looking for a reliable ride that\u2019s been well-loved and is totally ready for its next big adventure? This car is in really great shape and drives like a dream! It\u2019s been super dependable for me, and I\u2019m honestly so excited for its next owner to enjoy it as much as I have. It's the perfect companion for those daily commutes or fun weekend getaways. Feel free to reach out with any questions\u2014I'd love to see this go to a great home!",
      "price": 31500.0,
      "reputation": 0.4,
      "quality": "poor",
      "quality_value": 0.1,
      "timestep_posted": 34
    },
    {
      "id": "sybil_3_listing_2",
      "firm_id": "sybil_3",
      "description": "This E46 M3 is a driver-focused example featuring the high-revving S54 3.2L inline-six with its signature individual throttle bodies. Mechanically, the car has been addressed for long-term durability: the VANOS unit has been overhauled, and the rear subframe has been reinforced to mitigate common chassis fatigue. It sits on Bilstein B16 coilovers, enhancing the MacPherson strut front and multi-link rear geometry for superior lateral grip. Power is managed via a precise 6-speed Getrag manual transmission and the factory M-Variable limited-slip differential. Recent service includes a comprehensive valve adjustment and rod bearing replacement. While the finish shows light patina from spirited use, the drivetrain remains robust, delivering linear power and the raw feedback expected of a true analog sports car.",
      "price": 34500.0,
      "reputation": 0.6,
      "quality": "poor",
      "quality_value": 0.1,
      "timestep_posted": 34
    }
